            style="color: #0099cc;"></span></a><a href="#start_measurment">Réaliser
          une mesure</a></li>
      <span style="color: #0099cc;"> </span>
      <li><span style="color: #0099cc;"><a href="#give_a_description">Associer
            une description</a> </span> </li>
      <span style="color: #0099cc;"> </span>
      <li><span style="color: #0099cc;"><a href="#analyse_results">Analysez les
            résultats </a></span></li>
      <li><span style=" color: #0099cc;"><span style="color: #9e9e9e;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Explorer
              la carte</span></span> </span></li>
    </ol>
